## Technical Implementation Details

### Backend: OrdersGateway ([orders.gateway.ts](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/orders/orders.gateway.ts))
```typescript
@SubscribeMessage('joinRidersRoom')
handleJoinRidersRoom(client: Socket) {
  client.join('riders_room');
}

emitNewOrder(order: any) {
  this.server.to('riders_room').emit('newOrder', order);
}
```

### Rider App: Socket connection ([DashboardScreen.tsx](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/mobile-rider-app/src/screens/DashboardScreen.tsx))
```tsx
socket.on('newOrder', (order) => {
  setPendingOrders(prev => [order, ...prev]);
  Alert.alert('New Order!', 'A new delivery request is available nearby.');
});
```

### User App: Dynamic Rider Display ([OrderTrackingScreen.tsx](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/mobile-user-app/src/screens/OrderTrackingScreen.tsx))
```tsx
{rider && (
  <View style={styles.riderCard}>
    <Text style={styles.riderName}>{rider.name}</Text>
    {/* ... Call button and avatar ... */}
  </View>
)}
```

